  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954840/extras/d0309f85802050d9bb750478dd1b0536.avif?t=1723871191\" width=594 height=64 /></span><br><br><strong>Enter the simulation imagination (SI) room as Azula and recover her true strength throughout multiple terrains and challenges.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954840/extras/f6ff659639a990bb0209bada5ce682ec.poster.avif?t=1723871191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954840/extras/f6ff659639a990bb0209bada5ce682ec.webm?t=1723871191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954840/extras/f6ff659639a990bb0209bada5ce682ec.mp4?t=1723871191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954840/extras/e6859ed761cf3fcd43531a874ca30b50.avif?t=1723871191\" width=594 height=64 /></span><br><br><strong>Keep up the advantage by continuously hitting the enemy! Build up the combo counter to reach different levels of rewards!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954840/extras/96590e2d793c3303bdfde45c93e567e8.poster.avif?t=1723871191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954840/extras/96590e2d793c3303bdfde45c93e567e8.webm?t=1723871191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954840/extras/96590e2d793c3303bdfde45c93e567e8.mp4?t=1723871191\" type=\"vid